{"title":"Continuum. Presentaciones Atípicas de la Enfermedad de Alzheimer (EA)-2025","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Geriatría/Continuum. Presentaciones Atípicas de la Enfermedad de Alzheimer (EA)-2025.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Presentaciones Atípicas de la\\NEnfermedad de Alzheimer (EA)","guid":"PmDgszgOBM9GH08GP-ObSA","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Introducción","guid":"F4o7SCuw6jBOL9eNRyajag","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"🔹 EA clásica → Deterioro multidimensional, pero con predominio de afectación mnésica.","guid":"cB3QX2Z7jgt2ffgHMZqMIg","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"🔹 Presentaciones atípicas → Síntomas predominantes en dominios no relacionados con la memoria.","guid":"DWsLHUfd96lcKdxRAIeRBw","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"🔹 Variantes atípicas\\Ncon diferencias en:","guid":"F9vcKFW3xFkBeTntFhusug","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"• Clínica (síntomas específicos).","guid":"Y-fgkUc422s3N7nMcKMeIQ","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"4","text":"• Neuroimagen (patrones metabólicos en FDG-PET).","guid":"WKBTFmf_bkwRt4_jNGWT2g","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"4","text":"• Manejo (estrategias adaptadas a cada forma).","guid":"HmmRdXp_G1ZuQ2jTN6WCvA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"0","text":"Principales Variantes Atípicas de EA","guid":"EPpzoW57r-Yz4s8BCTPvrA","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"EA Posterior Cortical Atrófica\\N(PCA)","guid":"Jot7d1Q_DgY_zkxrFqlL1g","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"📍 Área afectada: Occipital y parietal.","guid":"OrqcETZMRHNIQ9f4SCWnLw","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"9","text":"🧠 Síntomas principales:","guid":"fio8HCRttEpIrTg2FgYYRQ","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"• Dificultades visuoespaciales y perceptivas.","guid":"eiV4o0omciMsIcT_Xg1ZNQ","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"• Agnosias visuales, problemas con orientación espacial.","guid":"EV9NjmNZfstOsHdWaf-gpQ","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"11","text":"• Dificultad con la lectura y procesamiento visual.","guid":"S1jtF2BoBzoeZTR_acJ-jA","children":[]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"9","text":"🖼 Neuroimagen: Hipometabolismo occipitoparietal con hiperactividad frontal.","guid":"WucikAyonVIhaAFJa-GWMQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"8","text":"Variante Logopénica de la\\NAfasia Primaria Progresiva\\N(lvPPA)","guid":"eyRNOVVK0Ep1FYXeIa_IsA","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"📍 Área afectada: Lóbulos temporal y parietal izquierdos.","guid":"KYneUTTj0kk4WRSGZER6Yg","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"16","text":"🧠 Síntomas principales:","guid":"azAWvACc7H8saiGRaVpS2Q","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"• Dificultad en recuperación de palabras.","guid":"JQqgyXUXWcd_YGseHzAZbA","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"18","text":"• Déficit en repetición de frases largas.","guid":"Pz3L6yuCMB19PXKhUJ0ZeQ","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"18","text":"• Preservación de gramática y articulación.","guid":"Dtuu6Evt6fg6nLoeWjSb_w","children":[]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"16","text":"🖼 Neuroimagen: Hipometabolismo en corteza temporal y parietal izquierda.","guid":"LFXxMlkB7p1D9xqMBz0Twg","children":[]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"8","text":"Demencia Frontotemporal\\NVariante Conductual\\N(bvFTD)","guid":"TJs7fi1BBG9n3oN6Wg6Jyw","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"📍 Área afectada: Lóbulo frontal.","guid":"ds1wzmRMQhxNLGQHJbj5Aw","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"23","text":"🧠 Síntomas principales:","guid":"U9iqsiEZF20PTm1XK5lDGg","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"• Conducta desinhibida, impulsividad.","guid":"d4Rsq10XrBsgcd2eCMd4SQ","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"25","text":"• Apatía o comportamientos repetitivos.","guid":"c1kvsx2SkPlVfybGfn0Zrw","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"25","text":"• Alteraciones del juicio y falta de introspección.","guid":"DFWwBgK2GOpzmsPXbBul4Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"23","text":"🖼 Neuroimagen: Hipometabolismo frontal con hiperactividad occipito-parietal.","guid":"L5xoIhHv-hZoZqKpWW-HDw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"30","parent":"0","text":"🔹 EA Disejecutiva (dAD)","guid":"PaDkRjaWejYglip6Z7q6LA","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"📍 Área afectada: Red frontoparietal ","guid":"FuMd3zMN-A0s0RmMLm1ZJw","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"Corteza de asociación heteromodal.","guid":"OqnsH2g0L9ICfqHZZDPKcA","children":[]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"30","text":"🧠 Síntomas:","guid":"Xr7iPXsA8Rl1k_ySHF_GhA","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"✔ Alteración de\\Nfunciones ejecutivas:","guid":"G7mi3xVrpsBDV6PEYngKlg","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"• ↓ planificación, organización y toma de decisiones.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"34","text":"• Déficit en memoria de trabajo y flexibilidad cognitiva.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"34","text":"• Tareas automatizadas conservadas, pero fallas en tareas cognitivamente demandantes.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"33","text":"• Alteraciones en toma de decisiones y multitareas.","guid":"afnALHEC1s9_r10UKTeMFw","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"33","text":"• “Olvido” de procesos o secuencias","guid":"Pm-JES3HlXUCzbv6M23vSw","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"• Deterioro percibido como pérdida de memoria, pero es fallo ejecutivo.","guid":"Vi13RRb8tzV8U1VzcecaJQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"33","text":"• Problemas con memoria de trabajo y flexibilidad cognitiva.","guid":"At2xMGKKTEB8PGP5I40eeg","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"33","text":"• Afectación en lenguaje (logopenia: anomia y dificultad en repetición).","guid":"Eb2y_zRZV6pchLEFXuEY9A","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"33","text":"• Problemas en orientación espacial.","guid":"RlAO3wGdE4RrDZWNQW728Q","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"33","text":"• Irritabilidad, ansiedad, depresión secundaria.","guid":"L9aQ9n3Fja1-KtcrRrmu1Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"30","text":"✔ Neuroimagen y\\Nbiomarcadores:","guid":"WHvoYmA6Eape7UhzGaMtNA","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"• PET-Tau / FDG-PET / MRI →\\Natrofia/disfunción en parietal y frontal.","guid":"TLp0gQWzduoyOy67fo-EKA","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"Hipometabolismo en áreas de asociación heteromodal,\\Nhiperactividad en cortezas motoras y sensoriales.","guid":"SNq5rTRxX68FlVHTdTCq3w","children":[]}]},{"id":"48","parent":"45","text":"• Hippocampo usualmente conservado en MRI.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"30","text":"📉 Impacto funcional:","guid":"MNOFuir78Ld1Jwf8D5Jn-A","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"• Pueden mantener tareas rutinarias y bien aprendidas (ej. conducir).","guid":"Jfzh0Wq7BI4r8i58V5RNIQ","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"49","text":"• Incapacidad para adaptarse a cambios tecnológicos o nuevos procesos.","guid":"AOUrmjAMryxP1IfsA8Lcyw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"0","text":"🔹 EA Variante Conductual (bvAD)","guid":"DXNOTEmMbF98bb6icx3aPA","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"📍 Área afectada: Lóbulo frontal, temporal medial y corteza cingulada.","guid":"LuuING-MaJZT7LNlaZV0VA","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"52","text":"🧠 Síntomas:","guid":"BXG_zm5DXO0IKUlgQ-FI3w","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"✔ Síntomas conductuales\\Npredominan:","guid":"dsdKCBLjWI1p8rX4EEtNPQ","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"• Alteraciones sociales, emocionales y motivacionales.","guid":"MxnQxy2iLhUhVgZWERmDSQ","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"55","text":"• Pérdida de control de impulsos y comportamientos inapropiados.","guid":"XIMleBjs7HRWH18_Ccf58Q","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"55","text":"→ Aquí la conducta es la causa del deterioro funcional.","guid":"CgS6MkPSwKZeLHPRBsRtxA","children":[]}]},{"id":"59","parent":"54","text":"• Alteraciones en conducta social → Desinhibición, impulsividad.","guid":"HAryYgr3BVp3TzgrS-GDWA","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"54","text":"• Apatía → Falta de motivación en actividades previas.","guid":"CLyTB3V6D1YSmzItOZAYwg","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"54","text":"• Embotamiento emocional → Disminución de respuestas afectivas.","guid":"IHYADgfCOipJIoC6RnLh3w","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"54","text":"• Alteraciones en reconocimiento emocional y empatía.","guid":"CyPp_G7DHwwtNvIkdR2qKA","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"54","text":"• Conductas repetitivas u obsesivas.","guid":"cn0-uHUUrzYeBy8Ac2JqUw","children":[]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"52","text":"📉 Impacto funcional:","guid":"JSFeYm3btux3JUceN7hZzg","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"• Pérdida de interés en higiene y cuidado personal.","guid":"Oeyi0R51QmNcDQg5OlbmYQ","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"• Conductas inapropiadas en contextos sociales.","guid":"IknurV9Cz5gBETjQJ7uuew","children":[]}]},{"id":"67","parent":"52","text":"✔ Neuroimagen y biomarcadores:","guid":"LFMjSC9BNTR0OF_mbVcpDg","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"• PET-Tau / FDG-PET / MRI → atrofia/disfunción en frontal medial.","guid":"SC4mwzGtkJ0Vi2VFPoM56Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"69","parent":"52","text":"🔹 dAD vs. bvAD → La disfunción ejecutiva es primaria en dAD, mientras que en bvAD los síntomas son motivacionales y emocionales.","guid":"TYYshQk6gjBrnPdaaZEe6A","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"52","text":"🔹 bvAD vs. bvFTD → Ambos pueden ser clínicamente indistinguibles. La diferencia radica en los biomarcadores (bvAD tiene patología de EA).","guid":"WGY-3EgN1G5WfjNTeNw-6g","children":[]}]},{"id":"71","parent":"0","text":"Manejo y\\NTratamiento","guid":"cP_UZHRqo7tzlBFJBbU3pw","children":[{"id":"72","parent":"71","text":"🔹 Farmacológico","guid":"UcDzhClDyO0_i_lNHPL6OQ","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"✔ Inhibidores de colinesterasa y antagonistas NMDA (como en EA típica).","guid":"VhjHrjEbFMAiEaPAIWMI0w","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"✔ Antidepresivos, ansiolíticos, antipsicóticos solo si es necesario (cuidado con sobremedicación).","guid":"frc4bWGHM6cO9zikK5Yrsg","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"72","text":"✔ Anticuerpos monoclonales antiamiloide → Datos limitados en variantes atípicas.","guid":"Ig38XyRHFvEl-0t8a89HRg","children":[]}]},{"id":"76","parent":"71","text":"🔹 No farmacológico","guid":"JTPsmAnxii9Jwhm4CQzxxA","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"✔ Educación a cuidadores y adaptación del entorno.","guid":"I1prIkSjBrtFTDXNBNEggw","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"76","text":"✔ Estrategias compensatorias para disfunción ejecutiva (checklists, evitar multitasking).","guid":"FgInEXpnuL82F-R8BwH7dQ","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"76","text":"✔ Técnicas de modificación de conducta en bvAD (redirección, evitar confrontaciones).","guid":"btJceymr9cUMtzMdQJNP_w","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"76","text":"✔ Apoyo psicológico para manejo de ansiedad e irritabilidad en dAD.","guid":"Uu--skxDLGpdhko5KQiGYQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"81","parent":"0","text":"Presentaciones\\NClínicas","guid":"ex7oETzSdY1Cuf_oQV7FCQ","children":[{"id":"82","parent":"81","text":"📌 Síndrome Disejecutivo Progresivo (SDP) y\\NEnfermedad de Alzheimer Disejecutiva (dAD)","guid":"aphQnybXsvkGgvWDacgJKw","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"1️⃣ Criterios Diagnósticos del SDP","guid":"bOi7NCXiN3Zoe2EXNiX7pA","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"✔ Síndrome Disejecutivo\\NProgresivo (SDP)","guid":"WoIAgXoHsHx9IELkNoVHMQ","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"• Declive persistente y predominante\\N(>6 meses) en funciones ejecutivas:","guid":"aZcNjSp0xt85w9piSwvDpQ","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"• ↓ Memoria de trabajo","guid":"KzKQiQXH6ddA23MKPUTp7g","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"85","text":"• ↓ Flexibilidad cognitiva","guid":"ZtDcnVVteT9piIpqPyeJaw","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"85","text":"• ↓ Inhibición","guid":"ShDeDnDs_X05RJKaae7mrA","children":[]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"84","text":"• Ausencia de síntomas conductuales prominentes (descarta variante conductual FTD).","guid":"frN5_S71KYsDOGNsB_bC7w","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"84","text":"• No atribuible a causas secundarias (psiquiátricas, cerebrovasculares, metabólicas, tóxicas, infecciosas).","guid":"UHfqBAIqB_F-IscVF9zh8g","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"83","text":"✔ Evidencia Clínica","guid":"c47H8kEmDfBOa3NYMX93eA","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"• Reportes de paciente o informante.","guid":"U-cJjhIwGgIgD0GwPn9aLQ","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"91","text":"• Evaluación cognitiva formal confirma déficit en tareas complejas → Manipulación abstracta/simultánea.","guid":"OQfM-yaSNzQoR2NYZDpdhA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"94","parent":"82","text":"2️⃣ Enfermedad de\\NAlzheimer Disejecutiva\\N(dAD)","guid":"fy-4jARa3ZB_RPRTVxNp3w","children":[{"id":"95","parent":"94","text":"✔ Posible dAD","guid":"EhJZZWEI8sYUkgY1LEOgfA","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"• Cumple criterios de SDP","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"95","text":"• Biomarcadores de EA positivos\\N(≥1 de los siguientes):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"• LCR: ↓ Aβ42 o Aβ42/Aβ40","guid":"LFohC2ki1mIhf0dyEyr9qA","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"97","text":"• PET amiloide: retención anormal.","guid":"PpBPogsH0dxSUocTCKEtsA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"100","parent":"94","text":"✔ Definitiva dAD","guid":"WFaszXSjZM8HZHMTeh0JLw","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"• Cumple criterios de posible dAD","guid":"e_TPWguXGa1ykBRceqhJVw","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"100","text":"• Evidencia patológica adicional\\N(≥1 de los siguientes):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"103","parent":"102","text":"• LCR: ↑ Tau fosforilada.","guid":"OoxDOXXId8kCnwxGCwQtPQ","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"102","text":"• PET-Tau: retención anormal.","guid":"d_J_ugDB01si4Q8vYYmNRw","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"102","text":"• Genética: mutación autosómica dominante EA.","guid":"KzaaO1yk6ZEslVDsfx2jyQ","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"102","text":"• Postmortem: diagnóstico confirmado.","guid":"btUDlEykkp09nP33J9zQjw","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"107","parent":"82","text":"📌 Resumen Final","guid":"YXS2GClyQq9YbD-gVQN-Cw","children":[{"id":"108","parent":"107","text":"✅ SDP → Diagnóstico clínico basado en deterioro progresivo de funciones ejecutivas.","guid":"H94InQ3GfIB1sJbxGUl8wA","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"107","text":"✅ Posible dAD → Confirmación con biomarcadores amiloides.","guid":"CUNI8SGCwHh-8aSEdiwEJg","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"107","text":"✅ Definitiva dAD → Evidencia adicional de patología tau/EA genética o autopsia.","guid":"R2T37mdtBZwsUf_KIeb4bw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"111","parent":"81","text":"📌 Comparación de EA Disejecutiva (dAD),\\NEA Variante Conductual (vAD) y FTD\\NVariante Conductual (bvFTD)","guid":"ZA5lnlHzzpBaSDjfVXI5xw","children":[{"id":"112","parent":"111","text":"🟢 Clínica","guid":"OJ5HYwUOb5gWOLUENJMWvQ","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"🔹 dAD → Sd. Disejecutivo progresivo (45-70 años)","guid":"EKWJRQjIyWEvO2AUSzHMfg","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"112","text":"🔹 vAD → Sd. Conductual progresivo (edad variable)","guid":"fpFBKjHabFtWNfm7doPA5A","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"112","text":"🔹 bvFTD → Sd. Conductual progresivo (40-65 años)","guid":"Mpw_tnkXCOtYDU4rXdLZ8Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"116","parent":"111","text":"🟢 Neuropsicológico","guid":"VbvyfASinxdc8H27RJD2EA","children":[{"id":"117","parent":"116","text":"🔹 dAD → Disfunción ejecutiva severa","guid":"czbJ0WXkYU8MFy4UH5Dq3A","children":[{"id":"118","parent":"117","text":"➥ ⚠ Puede parecer falsa validez baja en pruebas","guid":"UUcxtBqNe7JsbcagRH37hQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"119","parent":"116","text":"🔹 vAD → Memoria y función ejecutiva: normal o variable","guid":"AHHdAXiE9LRkDuZhT3kUsw","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"116","text":"🔹 bvFTD → Memoria y función ejecutiva: normal o variable","guid":"JhtqOhbKzuZdEJwHXrmxnQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"121","parent":"111","text":"🟢 Función social/emocional","guid":"G9k-fnNJUQwTTMhaLH7Hww","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"🔹 dAD → Secundaria, puede estar ausente","guid":"fBIabUKIKG93sJRCeqNblw","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"121","text":"🔹 vAD → Primaria, debe estar presente","guid":"dGKUyk3mjf1xJxx7Jv7UgA","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"121","text":"🔹 bvFTD → Primaria, debe estar presente","guid":"Rv2W6Ek0aqYE0a5yHLmJZQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"125","parent":"111","text":"🟢 Neuroimagen","guid":"TdcJvWHCLC1hSn91Hx47cg","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"🔹 dAD → Atrofia parietal predominante (córtex de asociación)","guid":"Rj06yUerHVlMOpmUbFilBA","children":[{"id":"127","parent":"126","text":"➥ Hipocampo preservado","guid":"fE-n3024RhVjnDb3fMGE4A","children":[]}]},{"id":"128","parent":"125","text":"🔹 vAD → Atrofia frontotemporal con extensión a temporal inferior y parietal","guid":"XnXsPylLNZtLElahek8qvQ","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"125","text":"🔹 bvFTD → Atrofia frontotemporal","guid":"HJSGp15fHvwmzfKAGKahFA","children":[]}]},{"id":"130","parent":"111","text":"🟢 Biomarcadores EA","guid":"IOdHax5-hsITSfyrFUncNQ","children":[{"id":"131","parent":"130","text":"🔹 dAD → Positivos","guid":"bGUUwARxGSY8SLC1M2KrqA","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"130","text":"🔹 vAD → Positivos","guid":"TaWDzEEaXydQHDUNG3yNig","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"130","text":"🔹 bvFTD → Negativos","guid":"ItyLVDFmtIM6msj8HywzMw","children":[]}]},{"id":"134","parent":"111","text":"📌 Resumen","guid":"WyZQA2V1JslGrq7_fA2Xbg","children":[{"id":"135","parent":"134","text":"✅ dAD → Disejecutivo puro. Parietal afectado. No síntomas conductuales prominentes","guid":"fx76mB42__Mb7bgURVw1Yg","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"134","text":"✅ vAD → Conductual prominente, pero con EA confirmada","guid":"ZeIdTGgoUagxtNpmRFgJiw","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"134","text":"✅ bvFTD → Conductual prominente, sin biomarcadores de EA","guid":"EXOHQ3zHMQc-pzRILggN6w","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"134","text":"🔹 dAD vs. bvAD → dAD afecta principalmente la ejecución cognitiva, mientras que bvAD afecta motivación y conducta.","guid":"XmnE0U2gJFkju230LA9Ing","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"134","text":"🔹 bvAD vs. bvFTD → Clínicamente similares, pero bvAD tiene biomarcadores de EA positivos, bvFTD no.","guid":"DrqDgHPXowFHi9YoMZcO1Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"140","parent":"81","text":"Neuroimagen y\\NBiomarcadores","guid":"TCbg1S3o0u4vxRnUIQAsmg","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"🔹 RM y FDG-PET","guid":"IF2fF2yw-hxpuYd_Bj-8ZA","children":[{"id":"142","parent":"141","text":"🧠 dAD → Hipometabolismo parietal y dorsolateral prefrontal.","guid":"VNlLxBtuYeVKl8XvZkzTCA","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"141","text":"🧠 bvAD → Hipometabolismo frontotemporal.","guid":"GDWS7Ak--jgUVODzc1vi8A","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"141","text":"🧠 bvFTD → Hipometabolismo frontal más focal.","guid":"brQhAVsDj_JvaXpecqfOjA","children":[]}]},{"id":"145","parent":"140","text":"🔹 Biomarcadores en LCR","guid":"NPw7nQDA7gJjAJDYE2YAbw","children":[{"id":"146","parent":"145","text":"✔ EA (dAD y bvAD) → ↓ Aβ42, ↑ Tau fosforilada.","guid":"TmESWwa7_sw_dUkNXRuV2w","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"145","text":"✔ FTD (bvFTD) → Sin patrón de EA.","guid":"epOhzQcBHzUOsqSwH9H5Ug","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"148","parent":"81","text":"Manejo y\\NTratamiento","guid":"CSe-WV915rlEL0tvKYVdcA","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"✔ Farmacológico","guid":"SVc003pc38QHTP-iYYzHvw","children":[{"id":"150","parent":"149","text":"• Inhibidores de colinesterasa y antagonistas NMDA.","guid":"A5vZ_Buh4JVU6Kqvck_6_Q","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"149","text":"• Antidepresivos y ansiolíticos (solo si es necesario).","guid":"dqVwh0RSJQ5k98mJK6GsJQ","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"149","text":"• Monoclonales antiamiloide (uso limitado en variantes atípicas).","guid":"RRMTEEf4WmE_B6yUE3Qlaw","children":[]}]},{"id":"153","parent":"148","text":"✔ No farmacológico","guid":"TrRZLX589aFwj7tGSUf6-w","children":[{"id":"154","parent":"153","text":"• Estrategias para compensar disfunción ejecutiva (checklists, evitar multitasking).","guid":"BX4U1n9CX_dpGfRNDqXTLw","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"153","text":"• Técnicas de modificación conductual en bvAD (redirección, evitar confrontación).","guid":"XrhGsC1JP7w4KzCfKt8nhQ","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"153","text":"• Educación a cuidadores y adaptación del entorno.","guid":"WzISqmfwSnRL31QfJIlHfQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"157","parent":"0","text":"Atrofia Cortical Posterior\\N(PCA):","guid":"DLs9kBFnd6swx7SAIRRxwg","children":[{"id":"158","parent":"157","text":"Introducción","guid":"TpnzOGhn0rsdJXdEVBgIDg","children":[{"id":"159","parent":"158","text":"🔹 PCA = Variante atípica de EA con predominio de alteraciones visuales.","guid":"bs40Vlr-uexYOP8xZXOk3g","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"158","text":"🔹 Disfunción cortical visual → Ocasionalmente confundida con problemas oftalmológicos.","guid":"H1De-j0wyLoRFVEDZGPyCg","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"158","text":"🔹 Relativa preservación de memoria, lenguaje, función ejecutiva y comportamiento en fases tempranas.","guid":"BSkjHFAc_Zd32Bd1U918SQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"162","parent":"157","text":"Presentación Clínica","guid":"Z6oysgY_a5Fivds9RmJ5Yg","children":[{"id":"163","parent":"162","text":"Síntomas Tempranos\\N(Primer Año)","guid":"M4irTRrpC9xxQaDoDrq99w","children":[{"id":"164","parent":"163","text":"🧠 Dificultad visual sin\\Ncausa oftalmológica","guid":"AtlWUD0g9QczRAV0ZSaAiA","children":[{"id":"165","parent":"164","text":"✔ Visión borrosa, problemas al leer.","guid":"EE1IyTlaFLFLD4S8fxt9Hw","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"164","text":"✔ Dificultad con pantallas\\N(computadora, celular).","guid":"FFjOnSNIg-1kjyH9M6mtlw","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"164","text":"✔ Problemas de contraste y\\Npercepción de objetos.","guid":"YHlMqHWkcwAYDZ-hZaJvxA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"168","parent":"162","text":"Síntomas Posteriores\\N(1-2 años)","guid":"RcFwlw_ltxY5f-wNFFtjzw","children":[{"id":"169","parent":"168","text":"✔ Persistencia de problemas visuales pese a cambio de lentes.","guid":"eE2J0ValY1Joc2vdX_e8hA","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"168","text":"✔ Dificultad para encontrar objetos aunque estén en el campo visual.","guid":"XOTO40sxRxomWjXmEG16MQ","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"168","text":"✔ Dificultad para leer señales de tráfico.","guid":"ZhpS9xeb1s4fKDgoaPOpRw","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"168","text":"✔ Problemas con tecnología (email, teléfono).","guid":"VLzL1lJsPZ1OGinQZQoUnw","children":[]}]},{"id":"173","parent":"162","text":"Síntomas Avanzados\\N(>2 años)","guid":"C8ZSThkproxkJZG-IB8g6w","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"✔ Alteración de la percepción de profundidad.","guid":"PHIyeki0s7xTyM6CHOt_Ig","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"173","text":"✔ Pérdida total de la capacidad de lectura y escritura.","guid":"PlkmvGvWbiMCje7mBBqXVA","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"173","text":"✔ Incapacidad para firmar documentos.","guid":"e7wlOTwN2vMYdfsjdAmvCg","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"173","text":"✔ Restricción de movilidad (ej. dificultad para conducir).","guid":"ErM-RQDpZwFUAWuOb5gNKQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"178","parent":"157","text":"Criterios Diagnósticos","guid":"TBquG3pboXUABYdaMjUBEg","children":[{"id":"179","parent":"178","text":"🔹\\\\/ Características centrales de PCA (se requieren 3):\\\\/","guid":"Efd4Qx8tv4IbKKpaZrREGQ","children":[{"id":"180","parent":"179","text":"✔ Déficit en\\Npercepción espacial.","guid":"cZn9H2lC1CpLvli4fWBPbQ","children":[{"id":"181","parent":"180","text":"✔ Simultagnosia\\N(síndrome de Balint).","guid":"AmyCti_j6ncdf3BYPt61MA","children":[{"id":"182","parent":"181","text":"✔ Agnosia\\Nde objetos.","guid":"eJieM3FIPtpbyjRSNvHE7w","children":[{"id":"183","parent":"182","text":"✔ Dispraxia\\Nconstructiva.","guid":"XR6s_V5YIzg7DFxDWNrSNg","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"184","parent":"179","text":"✔ Agnosia\\Nambiental.","guid":"GmX-LFOCV2dM5IFBLRk8cQ","children":[{"id":"185","parent":"184","text":"✔ Alexia.","guid":"VGu-aCDl7M8csUmaIIZsgw","children":[{"id":"186","parent":"185","text":"✔ Desorientación izquierda-derecha\\N(síndrome de Gerstmann).","guid":"G0GORBy20PRSu22WLTkGiA","children":[{"id":"187","parent":"186","text":"✔ Acalculia.","guid":"O-SQd23kF_AT7UqhLX6Nlg","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"188","parent":"179","text":"✔ Prosopagnosia\\Naperceptiva.","guid":"VybsGl-ro1oq3t0EWZNu0A","children":[{"id":"189","parent":"188","text":"✔ Agrafia.","guid":"D4-N0UheTVwYciQBCCgsBA","children":[{"id":"190","parent":"189","text":"✔ Defecto homónimo\\Ndel campo visual.","guid":"OaaMN3Q8WFM_GfDzFsU5NA","children":[{"id":"191","parent":"190","text":"✔ Agnosia\\Ndigital.","guid":"UpR7jHomTTdvoAtrbPp5uA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"192","parent":"179","text":"✔ Apraxia\\Noculomotora.","guid":"TaiknjyEjKwaE7YpIhRjBg","children":[{"id":"193","parent":"192","text":"✔ Ataxia\\Nóptica.","guid":"XWp5ezbE_8RCms-JeKwHwA","children":[{"id":"194","parent":"193","text":"✔ Apraxia de extremidades\\No del vestido.","guid":"U3vQuBVWPR8l5Q5ID2BhLw","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"195","parent":"178","text":"🔹\\\\/ Neuroimagen\\\\/","guid":"AzpVDznSWOk83u7GWmFBKQ","children":[{"id":"196","parent":"195","text":"✔ RM → Atrofia en regiones parieto-occipitales.","guid":"GX38Q2e9y8oz9K_6KQ2KFA","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"195","text":"✔ FDG-PET → Hipometabolismo en lóbulos occipitales y temporales.","guid":"MBwZJkxm0_sxNbYYacKlXQ","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"195","text":"✔ SPECT → Hipoperfusión en corteza posterior.","guid":"QKMsTnBPpwwAh96SEzen2g","children":[]}]},{"id":"199","parent":"178","text":"🔹 Características preservadas\\N(deben estar presentes)","guid":"anX0Q3An6f0AMiGSOB6Y4Q","children":[{"id":"200","parent":"199","text":"✔ Memoria episódica conservada.","guid":"LKx2qRpF17xaMvvnChbwJA","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"199","text":"✔ Lenguaje y función ejecutiva preservados\\N(en etapas iniciales).","guid":"UQrXgBzNy3ACwvfkJIaoOA","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"199","text":"✔ Personalidad y comportamiento intactos.","guid":"MiQIkCioBiwz5wloNV5dnw","children":[]}]},{"id":"203","parent":"178","text":"🔹 Exclusión\\Nde otras causas","guid":"YnpfFnDF-C4Pv57Je_hbWQ","children":[{"id":"204","parent":"203","text":"✔ ❌ No debe haber lesión estructural,\\Nisquemia o patología oftalmológica primaria.","guid":"WIPD-EO0TsMlBeVuCJ_dHg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"205","parent":"157","text":"Clasificación","guid":"EBsivlY7m4ZyYoJ8UL5PDA","children":[{"id":"206","parent":"205","text":"🔹 Nivel 1 → Diagnóstico clínico de PCA.","guid":"RotCknLqYQ5j9fbnMQE21Q","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"205","text":"🔹 Nivel 2 →","guid":"YCCXDhyYqb1z_2_uEkSfng","children":[{"id":"208","parent":"207","text":"• PCA-puro → Sin otras comorbilidades neurodegenerativas.","guid":"YxJLC2QoGHlpH8-2D77BtA","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"207","text":"• PCA-plus → Asociación con otras patologías (DLB, CBD, etc.).","guid":"fm3wNUNSy50Z1bHYT3jHtQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"210","parent":"205","text":"🔹 Nivel 3 →","guid":"RUCv6SfmeVZHov09J7sO_w","children":[{"id":"211","parent":"210","text":"• PCA-AD → Confirmación con biomarcadores de EA.","guid":"GKxxhFdinAYjs2pZcTA1fA","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"210","text":"• PCA definitiva → Confirmación en autopsia.","guid":"GxbqyUi5T8d50BKaKzINhw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"213","parent":"157","text":"Evaluación Clínica y\\NNeuropsicológica","guid":"HvTrTWwylRZ78FyUZYAt4A","children":[{"id":"214","parent":"213","text":"🔹 Pruebas clínicas\\Nútiles para detección:","guid":"VF7P-RkLh7s3t7Qjb3W6ww","children":[{"id":"215","parent":"214","text":"✔ Poppleeruter-Ghent → Percepción de figuras superpuestas.","guid":"Xxz2JF_mU3sWgWS1Qi9BLw","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"214","text":"✔ Juicio de orientación de líneas → Déficit en percepción espacial.","guid":"RA5r9H-hNGxR7gLjQnxcKg","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"214","text":"✔ Navon figures → Simultagnosia.","guid":"QvQACWvDtLwR9SPfIxSXFw","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"214","text":"✔ Cookie Theft Picture (Boston Aphasia Exam) → Evaluación de percepción y praxis.","guid":"CFxeeQX0k801WTa1TZ0OYg","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"214","text":"✔\\\\/ Test de copias de figuras (Pentágonos, Rey-Osterrieth) → Apraxia constructiva.\\\\/","guid":"LdsNI3z8M_N1WB1iRod-pw","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"214","text":"✔ Búsqueda visual → Evaluación de atención y procesamiento visual.","guid":"YcTXgjGHxr4ap8hKALnCzw","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"214","text":"✔ Letras fragmentadas → Evaluación de percepción de objetos.","guid":"Hbpb1BaYJN5mOfCvfNdR-Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"222","parent":"157","text":"Manejo","guid":"dn54WXy7VWU_BpMoOozkTg","children":[{"id":"223","parent":"222","text":"✔ Farmacológico","guid":"fFyJ0RD0lgx9CUB4P1CJ2g","children":[{"id":"224","parent":"223","text":"• Inhibidores de colinesterasa y antagonistas NMDA (como en EA).","guid":"FLqLmkgJ1QUJVYPwaRlblA","children":[]},{"id":"225","parent":"223","text":"• Manejo de ansiedad y depresión (ISRS si es necesario).","guid":"YRVcwEENOBNYjxZXQto0Qg","children":[]}]},{"id":"226","parent":"222","text":"✔ No farmacológico","guid":"fLhKyA7-ZFdiZSDyBRSpQQ","children":[{"id":"227","parent":"226","text":"• Adaptación del entorno → Mayor iluminación, contrastes en objetos.","guid":"cpT-0XM23qFDk_cSEE9apg","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"226","text":"• Terapias de rehabilitación visual → Aprendizaje de estrategias compensatorias.","guid":"Cc8DgCnN58ENJqyfAE172Q","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"226","text":"• Asesoramiento y soporte a cuidadores.","guid":"Jok9JkwtP8c62mAnIuXG9w","children":[]}]},{"id":"230","parent":"222","text":"✔ Evaluación para terapias antiamiloide (según criterios de EA).","guid":"FPL4JRe-V6dSsbejQs4FSA","children":[]}]},{"id":"231","parent":"157","text":"Pronóstico y Progresión","guid":"XSHV0zfjoJ9iNlDSWdogmw","children":[{"id":"232","parent":"231","text":"✔ Evolución hacia demencia en todos los casos.","guid":"RuIE90SbccRe7sncW9T9HA","children":[]},{"id":"233","parent":"231","text":"✔ Supervivencia media: 8-10 años.","guid":"XFnJazGggYAeowJkcRRVBg","children":[]},{"id":"234","parent":"231","text":"✔ Progresión de síntomas visuales antes que deterioro global.","guid":"eapWhSf4hlRaLbCaWr-zRg","children":[]},{"id":"235","parent":"231","text":"✔ Eventual afectación de memoria, lenguaje y conducta en fases tardías.","guid":"aQW-aDK8xvEdmeeIW5q9OQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"236","parent":"0","text":"Afasia Primaria Progresiva\\N(APP)","guid":"W8VAwzZqIyhox4tzOd3U-Q","children":[{"id":"237","parent":"236","text":"Definición \\NAfasia Primaria Progresiva\\NAPP","guid":"CvvGXHkQxH4wECTsMYUDgg","children":[{"id":"238","parent":"237","text":"Síndrome de demencia de origen neurodegenerativo\\Nque afecta de forma predominante y temprana el lenguaje.","guid":"RT4ERmrqhRNUasp6Il_aGQ","children":[]},{"id":"239","parent":"237","text":"• Criterios de Mesulam: Deterioro del lenguaje como dominio primario;\\Nprogresión y relativa conservación de otras áreas cognitivas al inicio.","guid":"Is4lszahG0x8Ofq1abAqqg","children":[]}]},{"id":"240","parent":"236","text":"Subtipos Principales","guid":"ezyNEFsoxJFFhSfGV5ZWew","children":[{"id":"241","parent":"240","text":"1. Logopénico","guid":"dNgw0H8RaAE5UNnYGDlMCg","children":[{"id":"242","parent":"241","text":"• Alteración en recuperación de palabras\\N(↓ fluencia por anomia).","guid":"DMlGEWQoKipIqquBBnOclw","children":[{"id":"243","parent":"242","text":"• Gramática y comprensión de\\Npalabras relativamente preservadas.","guid":"DCCwfyLYXBthM0_ddSZu5w","children":[]}]},{"id":"244","parent":"241","text":"• Dificultad en repetición de oraciones\\Nextensas.","guid":"VZUjDH7NN2VQwSwge4jInw","children":[{"id":"245","parent":"244","text":"• Atrofia generalmente asimétrica en el lóbulo temporal\\Nsuperior y unión temporoparietal del hemisferio dominante.","guid":"X_sWADyrRAArS3GxavbcXA","children":[]}]},{"id":"246","parent":"241","text":"• Con frecuencia asociado a patología Alzheimer (~70%).","guid":"NbwIfltblp0ce9_eevoMxA","children":[]}]},{"id":"247","parent":"240","text":"2. Agramática","guid":"QSdE0WyAYtcmxi53GJgBhw","children":[{"id":"248","parent":"247","text":"• Deterioro en la gramática de la producción del lenguaje.","guid":"RkYbsXDmqlgdWebeaRRBZA","children":[{"id":"249","parent":"248","text":"• Comprensión de palabras sencillas\\Nrelativamente preservada.","guid":"J4fFpBmT4ZNSxGwOIsRStA","children":[]}]},{"id":"250","parent":"247","text":"• Atrofia en la región frontoinferior del hemisferio dominante\\N(área de Broca).","guid":"dLymJBhJk9R6WqkwAYXsNg","children":[]},{"id":"251","parent":"247","text":"• Suele relacionarse con FTLD-tau.","guid":"fHG9_kMFVLEH-YjNCJJufQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"252","parent":"240","text":"3. Semántica","guid":"MdUPp19hnTcWSfHlASZnxQ","children":[{"id":"253","parent":"252","text":"• Deterioro en la comprensión de palabras (semántica).","guid":"Zd2wzWks2Kp9uN1kO3LT2Q","children":[{"id":"254","parent":"253","text":"• Gramática y repetición relativamente preservadas.","guid":"Z_oQD056CYU2-5x4R_UmDw","children":[]}]},{"id":"255","parent":"252","text":"• Atrofia predominante en la región\\Ntemporal anterior del hemisferio dominante.","guid":"CyVNhWJHDioy7AJrQOFWAw","children":[]},{"id":"256","parent":"252","text":"• Suele asociarse a FTLD-TDP.","guid":"PaKkx09n4ko722LIA-jAeA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"257","parent":"236","text":"APP Logopénica\\N(lvPPA)","guid":"QE6Molk1SaZs_QHcZ9ZSRw","children":[{"id":"258","parent":"257","text":"Características\\NClínicas","guid":"cskrOT_BbeoKmqT7Z4XRXQ","children":[{"id":"259","parent":"258","text":"• Logopenia → Pausas prolongadas, dificultad para encontrar palabras de baja frecuencia.","guid":"WAsBvgT1TitpC72TVHy_vQ","children":[]},{"id":"260","parent":"258","text":"• Repetición de frases largas alterada.","guid":"R_qi3XEFRmBdDy46LdhTqg","children":[]},{"id":"261","parent":"258","text":"• Comprensión de palabras y gramática relativamente conservadas.","guid":"WjIfClrIC59pSyeDQiwvGg","children":[]},{"id":"262","parent":"258","text":"• Al inicio, la atrofia o hipometabolismo puede ser sutil → Diagnóstico tardío.","guid":"KUIVJCBGw_wKIVUpNGdiqQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"263","parent":"257","text":"Patología\\NSubyacente","guid":"Ao3SJj0NV5V1SLisQDB27Q","children":[{"id":"264","parent":"263","text":"• Frecuentemente asociada a Enfermedad de Alzheimer (EA) (Aβ y tau).","guid":"DHU53zEkG3REGTdmTMPGgQ","children":[]},{"id":"265","parent":"263","text":"• Biomarcadores AD (PET amiloide, LCR) → Elevación de tau y/o ↓ Aβ42.","guid":"ClllGjEWOUI0mhjIfSKQUw","children":[]}]},{"id":"266","parent":"257","text":"Evolución y\\NPronóstico","guid":"RCoL7020H0QdX2ioDCSuzA","children":[{"id":"267","parent":"266","text":"• Progresión gradual → Afectación de más dominios cognitivos.","guid":"PrllpXpuluM5_QJ2GOuErw","children":[]},{"id":"268","parent":"266","text":"• Difícil dar un pronóstico preciso → Velocidad de declive variable.","guid":"Q47t9mU5CPMy4BpPRhzAHA","children":[]}]},{"id":"269","parent":"257","text":"Manejo y\\NTratamiento","guid":"IkZgiCgo0vsGTTcJLruaZw","children":[{"id":"270","parent":"269","text":"• Intervenciones\\Nno farmacológicas","guid":"WUzucEpmbm97f2DoY6ZTig","children":[{"id":"271","parent":"270","text":"• Terapia del habla y lenguaje (ej. Communication Bridge).","guid":"e3ynsjAZebFgyOPebFRO3w","children":[]},{"id":"272","parent":"270","text":"• Apoyo multidisciplinario (neurología, psicología, terapia ocupacional).","guid":"b043dUVxRY81NvfKM3hDZA","children":[]},{"id":"273","parent":"270","text":"• Educación y soporte a cuidadores → Afrontamiento de problemas de comunicación.","guid":"EyVk01KWYHM_nPIxUd7KeA","children":[]}]},{"id":"274","parent":"269","text":"• Farmacológico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"275","parent":"274","text":"• Inhibidores de colinesterasa y memantina → Eficacia limitada, sin evidencia concluyente.","guid":"TQT3VnmZ9Kdqyk8oIjuZ2A","children":[]},{"id":"276","parent":"274","text":"• Terapias antiamiloide (p. ej. anticuerpos monoclonales) → Pocos datos en lvPPA.","guid":"HOIeoUXiAvEgtFF-YHEMlw","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"277","parent":"236","text":"Diagnóstico\\NDiferencial","guid":"KxsL5FOUa80mjcyzTWFsbA","children":[{"id":"278","parent":"277","text":"• Subtipos mixtos → Combinación de rasgos semánticos/agramáticos/logopénicos.","guid":"J7XhbRl5ZKFfEmi9FwQY4g","children":[]}]},{"id":"279","parent":"236","text":"Factores de Riesgo\\Ny Disparidades","guid":"XuqqMBRJYIhKfFxGchAPAw","children":[{"id":"280","parent":"279","text":"• APOE ε4 → Menor asociación en PPA vs. EA típica.","guid":"A7NDHy65KKRWIFIpIJVhwA","children":[]},{"id":"281","parent":"279","text":"• Historia de dificultades de aprendizaje → Mayor prevalencia en PPA.","guid":"dJsrlXbUo6cBBm5YH7Y3eg","children":[]},{"id":"282","parent":"279","text":"• Edad de inicio más joven (<65 años) → Mayor impacto laboral y familiar.","guid":"SmkPdCeUOwttF6PmRiZOPA","children":[]},{"id":"283","parent":"279","text":"• Desigualdades de acceso → Diagnóstico tardío y barreras financieras para poblaciones vulnerables.","guid":"VG8-yGk0qrobMHt1S7Cw9Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"284","parent":"0","text":"PUNTOS CLAVE","guid":"bRCpdQFiT0I1bqRWShiLXA","children":[{"id":"285","parent":"284","text":"Atrofia Cortical Posterior\\N(PCA-AD)","guid":"YadYVh5LwMsCym2cfUImMw","children":[{"id":"286","parent":"285","text":"✔ Disfunción visual predominante con memoria, juicio e insight preservados inicialmente.","guid":"Y4-dJmPuYyB5rgaFfLR1uA","children":[]},{"id":"287","parent":"285","text":"✔ Presentación inicial común → Consulta oftalmológica por problemas visuales con examen ocular normal.","guid":"A4Ejd36g2rsDM68kQJUXXw","children":[]},{"id":"288","parent":"285","text":"✔ Síntomas iniciales:","guid":"Ix67tVX385gvc59gMaQFuw","children":[{"id":"289","parent":"288","text":"• Dificultad para leer 📖.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"290","parent":"288","text":"• Problemas de percepción espacial y objetual.","guid":"X2s4z115Ii5V_rJuJ64Cpw","children":[]},{"id":"291","parent":"288","text":"• Síndrome de Balint o Gerstmann.","guid":"Pe-mMVsEv5oE7hAIOdkwmg","children":[]}]},{"id":"292","parent":"285","text":"✔ Errores diagnósticos frecuentes:","guid":"ZxFSGTb8fHU0SgdEem6kIw","children":[{"id":"293","parent":"292","text":"• Diagnóstico retrasado por síntomas visuales iniciales, edad joven y buen desempeño global.","guid":"DbAM40GViPo77_4KG7OEDA","children":[]}]},{"id":"294","parent":"285","text":"✔ Criterios diagnósticos (2017) → ≥3 de 16 características.","guid":"CxRm7y7EA28-yRJZAduw9w","children":[]},{"id":"295","parent":"285","text":"✔ Neuroimagen y\\Nbiomarcadores:","guid":"Qadb_Si7yFESJv40bfp_RQ","children":[{"id":"296","parent":"295","text":"• MRI / FDG-PET / SPECT → atrofia posterior, hipometabolismo occipital-parietal.","guid":"TvHNRHpL_3o9F9rvAgueDA","children":[]},{"id":"297","parent":"295","text":"• PET-Tau → depósitos en occipital/posterior.","guid":"J-4tj15t4UUTJSFVBHFTCA","children":[]}]},{"id":"298","parent":"285","text":"✔ Clasificación:","guid":"V_z9hQZfXhpbUahTOaRV2w","children":[{"id":"299","parent":"298","text":"• PCA-Puro → Sin otra síndrome asociada.","guid":"d1rNuWlEgJUOOUz5AV-H6w","children":[]},{"id":"300","parent":"298","text":"• PCA-Plus → Asociado a corticobasal u otra patología.","guid":"LRdBO2xlwMsII_WwdUVn_w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"301","parent":"284","text":"Afasia Primaria Progresiva\\NLogopénica (lvPPA)","guid":"JKse5V4cFe825nwOCDq8Cw","children":[{"id":"302","parent":"301","text":"✔ Déficit principal:","guid":"Qgp5DzCUgpQE7zHERYuchg","children":[{"id":"303","parent":"302","text":"• Fallos en recuperación de palabras en lenguaje espontáneo y denominación.","guid":"HhNRaB2vWvUzyKHoXAL3mQ","children":[]},{"id":"304","parent":"302","text":"• Repetición alterada en frases largas.","guid":"eLQakDi2sfAV3Cg0WB9TXw","children":[]},{"id":"305","parent":"302","text":"• Comprensión y gramática relativamente preservadas.","guid":"Fi_UH2va2qJ_zVYGI9_hAg","children":[]}]},{"id":"306","parent":"301","text":"✔ Neuroimagen y\\Nbiomarcadores:","guid":"LzVdTwgi4OgGILPlUlQZBA","children":[{"id":"307","parent":"306","text":"• Atrofia en temporal superior y unión temporoparietal izquierda.","guid":"LXBjnDu9VBA_k2UPfGIw4Q","children":[]},{"id":"308","parent":"306","text":"• PET-Tau / FDG-PET → hipometabolismo en la red del lenguaje.","guid":"NglTinyrP_5-bc7tXfeBGg","children":[]}]},{"id":"309","parent":"301","text":"✔ Diagnóstico difícil:","guid":"XhrUgDWUU0UD-B7ARSwmmg","children":[{"id":"310","parent":"309","text":"• Paciente puede compensar usando lenguaje simplificado.","guid":"WxkhQxGS8EJiaNQiUnPu_Q","children":[]},{"id":"311","parent":"309","text":"• Pruebas neuropsicológicas pueden subestimar déficit si dependen del lenguaje.","guid":"etdw13CiIRtT03boJ-6yEw","children":[]}]},{"id":"312","parent":"301","text":"✔ Factores de riesgo:","guid":"bJDPujhCJgQ_msq9d6U2qQ","children":[{"id":"313","parent":"312","text":"• APOE ε4 NO tan relevante como en EA típica.","guid":"XQfh5lv3bJgdNBoSexszTw","children":[]}]},{"id":"314","parent":"301","text":"✔ Manejo:","guid":"ZwYpdH5j3RZ5gOegKK2FcQ","children":[{"id":"315","parent":"314","text":"• Terapia del habla (ensayos en curso).","guid":"eabHjlD8u_pXHiroclriHg","children":[]},{"id":"316","parent":"314","text":"• Soporte multidisciplinario → Psicología, neurología, terapia ocupacional.","guid":"CbNt62z6UxxKejV9H-NCCg","children":[]}]}]}]}]},"node_count":316,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Geriatría","filename":"Continuum. Presentaciones Atípicas de la Enfermedad de Alzheimer (EA)-2025","id":"map_926","resolved_references":[]}